data.description: Beautiful curb appeal, corner lot home.  Close to all Virginia and the Quad Cities have to offer.  Very well maintained, 4 bedroom home, including a sauna in the basement with a shower.  Unique open cabinets in the kitchen, and a pantry for all your cooking needs.  Open concept from the kitchen to the front entry, with all new windows in 2020. Schedule your showing today!
